{"tid":414193,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[好用] Chrome NewTab既Todo Manager!","createTime":"2017-09-26T04:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T13:31:35.000Z","uid":86302,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7719c0bb61098f2ef2fecac488bf250c51ac3475","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"小弟修讀電腦工程三年級，臨近搵intern既季節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要知道programmer工好注重CV有無projects，所以小弟寫咗個小小既chrome extension出黎。我都唔怕老實講，想借大家推下下載量同reviews。不過當然，用完幾日唔鍾意可以uninstall。亦都好歡迎大家比意見。小弟搵唔搵到好工就靠大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣點：<br />\n-簡約設計<br />\n-每次開新tab你既todos就係眼前，無得你唔記得<br />\n-可以drag and drop整理你既Todo list<br />\n-可以repeat task (e.g. 逢星期一三五remind你一次)<br />\n-免費，無廣告，而且係open source既(<a href=\"https://github.com/donfour/Committed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdonfour%2FCommitted&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b54f520f\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/donfour/Committed</a>)，有無惡意程式一目了然，可以安心使用<br />\n-個extension得736KB，佔好少位<br />\n<br />\nChrome Store連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/committed-newtab-todo-and/mffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb?hl=en-GB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fcommitted-newtab-todo-and%2Fmffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb%3Fhl%3Den-GB&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6e191d48\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/committed-newtab-todo-and/mffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb?hl=en-GB</a><br />\n<br />\nExtension截圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113850_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113850_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=f97ec802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=877f4551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=e4168afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=189ca2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=c93b0cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫忙我無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過小弟學programming兩年，web development一年多，識得C++, Java, Python, JavaScript (HTML CSS jQuery React Redux MongoDB)，對於想大學修讀電腦或者初學programming既你可以比少少advice。有高手ching係度我亦會虛心求指教同意見，多謝大家。"},{"pid":"f32bb74875e126cb71e52ac96f37c91f7ca85584","tid":414193,"uid":121087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"無down 未試<br />\n<br />\n但作為todos 應該要用顏色highlight important 既task"},{"pid":"8bcc78e682b24f463f784e9000e09691b6eb27bd","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無down 未試<br />\n<br />\n但作為todos 應該要用顏色highlight important 既task</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到<br />\n<br />\n可能遲d直頭可以custom較背景、字體顏色添"},{"pid":"48112120b42061f0c1d65e2b15be46d3d315b42d","tid":414193,"uid":21696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T07:17:32.000Z","msg":"留名支持一下"},{"pid":"8adf7f5ed15d7129c2988f1fd69d26507ad8fdf7","tid":414193,"uid":108937,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"github source?"},{"pid":"e591f53477fc3b9bd4eb6b26cfbd115e7732f15f","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>github source?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/donfour/Committed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdonfour%2FCommitted&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b54f520f\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/donfour/Committed</a>"},{"pid":"dc3098f04b2be3f50d350f513264c099703bb3e1","tid":414193,"uid":48993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d39fa1be6152a2f765b0c1cdd8a504723d57b09f","tid":414193,"uid":65859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔同 device sync 到？"},{"pid":"c7eff152f77b1b1ab78c9c9580ab14a62dc8e27e","tid":414193,"uid":33883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"唔多用Chrome, 又用緊Remember the Milk, 又Org-Mode for emacs, 不了!"},{"pid":"14c2a9df83322465303537038515d7d4fe3990d0","tid":414193,"uid":104613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05311555f5a948da88f028683eac48dbe395b146","tid":414193,"uid":9248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"學過下寫browser extension <br />\n寫咗個mon post extension 之後就無再研究落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔知寫咩去增加自己portfolio 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c029153518ba9