u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=877f4551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=e4168afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=189ca2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=c93b0cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫忙我無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過小弟學programming兩年，web development一年多，識得C++, Java, Python, JavaScript (HTML CSS jQuery React Redux MongoDB)，對於想大學修讀電腦或者初學programming既你可以比少少advice。有高手ching係度我亦會虛心求指教同意見，多謝大家。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀緊書寫到呢個level都唔差<br />\n<br />\n巴打分番開 component , container 會唔會之後好改啲? <br />\nextends Component instead React.Component 會唔會打少啲字<br />\n試下用map 唔好用 forloop<br />\n你個todo list 應該有state <br />\ngoogle 下 action creator, action, reducer, redux, react-redux, <br />\n而家有小小未發輝到react 世界威力<br />\n定係用 其他technology 會好啲?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你而家係P 仔比呢個app 我review, <br />\n我就會比上面啲suggestion<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論, 講錯請指正"},{"pid":"c064688ff55001f9a5d1fbc92d28d3bc6611a67b","tid":414193,"uid":40790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:06:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d50f5bf07855887eede73777a0b2f027acda881c","tid":414193,"uid":34301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"我想寫個js automation bot<br />\n用來block下廣告同自動填form咁<br />\n請問除咗js有冇咩要識？<br />\n係咪都要學下html5啲API?<br />\n<br />\n唔該"},{"pid":"9499b18f79dc317d9013bacecb961e59ca60a692","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔同 device sync 到？</blockquote><br />\n理論上係得既，不過好多功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd66bcfbd19d255ef3f6a3c7fd54d4a32acba6f9","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔多用Chrome, 又用緊Remember the Milk, 又Org-Mode for emacs, 不了!</blockquote><br />\n無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出面實有寫得好過我既，我當練習姐"},{"pid":"4969eec664d9deb3bfbc12539f662b45253a409f","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放咩tool?</blockquote><br />\n意思係用咩library寫? React做front end囉"},{"pid":"c858bd5b98739436dcdfa6c0f107446763eeb79f","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟修讀電腦工程三年級，臨近搵intern既季節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要知道programmer工好注重CV有無projects，所以小弟寫咗個小小既chrome extension出黎。我都唔怕老實講，想借大家推下下載量同reviews。不過當然，用完幾日唔鍾意可以uninstall。亦都好歡迎大家比意見。小弟搵唔搵到好工就靠大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣點：<br />\n-簡約設計<br />\n-每次開新tab你既todos就係眼前，無得你唔記得<br />\n-可以drag and drop整理你既Todo list<br />\n-可以repeat task (e.g. 逢星期一三五remind你一次)<br />\n-免費，無廣告，而且係open source既(<a href=\"https://github.com/donfour/Committed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdonfour%2FCommitted&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b54f520f\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/donfour/Committed</a>)，有無惡意程式一目了然，可以安心使用<br />\n-個extension得736KB，佔好少位<br />\n<br />\nChrome Store連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/committed-newtab-todo-and/mffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb?hl=en-GB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fcommitted-newtab-todo-and%2Fmffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb%3Fhl%3Den-GB&d=YYUhF8%2F1gLMKNsAr01a8F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6e191d48\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/committed-newtab-todo-and/mffcogdacgpjnckjepacaicfliaocneb?hl=en-GB</a><br />\n<br />\nExtension截圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113850_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113850_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=f97ec802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113856_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=877f4551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113904_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=e4168afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113913_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=189ca2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F113918_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=c93b0cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫忙我無以為報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過小弟學programming兩年，web development一年多，識得C++, Java, Python, JavaScript (HTML CSS jQuery React Redux MongoDB)，對於想大學修讀電腦或者初學programming既你可以比少少advice。有高手ching係度我亦會虛心求指教同意見，多謝大家。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀緊書寫到呢個level都唔差<br />\n<br />\n巴打分番開 component , container 會唔會之後好改啲? <br />\nextends Component instead React.Component 會唔會打少啲字<br />\n試下用map 唔好用 forloop<br />\n你個todo list 應該有state <br />\ngoogle 下 action creator, action, reducer, redux, react-redux, <br />\n而家有小小未發輝到react 世界威力<br />\n定係用 其他technology 會好啲?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你而家係P 仔比呢個app 我review, <br />\n我就會比上面啲suggestion<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論, 講錯請指正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳細呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會注意嫁啦<br />\nredux你講得啱，係我最初以為細project唔想set up咁多野<br />\n故事教訓我地，係唔係都落埋redux實唔錯"},{"pid":"efc117fbaff390f95f1a4262d5b9181f73226fa1","tid":414193,"uid":129573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲SIDE PROJECT 啲人唔會理<br />\n反而你做過咩靚公司 讀過咩靚學校更加實際<br />\n不過支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed4c36497ed9654ef7a948c45f5f64ced46ba05","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想寫個js automation bot<br />\n用來block下廣告同自動填form咁<br />\n請問除咗js有冇咩要識？<br />\n係咪都要學下html5啲API?<br />\n<br />\n唔該</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照計應該無咩其他野要識嫁啦wor<br />\n有個js library叫Robot.js可以控制你電腦輸入，鑽研下直頭可以寫隻好似以前online game個種掛機自動打怪外掛"},{"pid":"f55350847a3848f966a703fd691caf5c28566ea3","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢啲SIDE PROJECT 啲人唔會理<br />\n反而你做過咩靚公司 讀過咩靚學校更加實際<br />\n不過支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無cv點有靚公司請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不要再說了"},{"pid":"ca9a939bfb09549c1018915748f9cc77f779e360","tid":414193,"uid":86302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學過下寫browser extension <br />\n寫咗個mon post extension 之後就無再研究落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔知寫咩去增加自己portfolio 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講係要盡量令自己技能多元化d<br />\n寫完front end，再去學back end server，再去學寫database<br />\n就算front end呀都要去掂多幾個framework，咩angular呀vue呀<br />\n跟住仲未講mobile<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}